{"tid":1516281,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【閒說】想做一名成功的小說家","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:22:48.000Z","uid":314617,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cec3adf696a963a2d32f8d9b27a99e63b56e8ef","tid":1516281,"uid":314617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"話說，小弟想當一名成功的小說家。<br />\n不是說那些在網絡平台上寂寂無名的人，而是那些有人支持、有人鼓勵，而且得到迴響、共鳴的作家。<br />\n不過，現在距離成功，恐怕還有一段很長的距離&hellip;<br />\n在小弟心中，希望總會有成功。<br />\n但在成功之前，還想得到更多的支持。<br />\n所以小弟就選擇了這裡作為萌牙的地方。<br />\n（說穿了，其實在紙言平台上也能找到小弟的足跡喔！傳送門在這裡：<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/authors/40268.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fauthors%2F40268.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b6ccbe16\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/authors/40268.html</a>）<br />\n<br />\n最後，還是這一句：<strong>請多多指教。</strong>"},{"pid":"073e07e56c5f940bf9bf0619a05c6537fe0fbc85","tid":1516281,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae39ec36cbb8f7508598ba8bfe7e9b641c5efd40","tid":1516281,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" 